Usage: editCutWire [-help] [-only_visible_wires] [-selected] {-lines {x1 y1 x2 y2 ...} | [-box {x1 y1 x2 y2} [-delete_wire_in_box ]] }

-help                        # Prints out the command usage
-box {x1 y1 x2 y2}           # Specify the lower left and upper right
                             # coordinates of the cutting box (box, optional)
-delete_wire_in_box          # Specify to delete cutted wire (bool, optional)
-lines {x1 y1 x2 y2 ...}     # Specify the coordinates of both cutting lines
                             # ends (box_list, optional)
-only_visible_wires          # Specify to cut visible wires only
                             # (bool, optional)
-selected                    # Cut the selected wires (bool, optional)